Title:          evilvte.tcz
Description:    VTE based, highly customizable terminal emulator.
Version:        0.4.6
Author:         Wen-Yen Chuang
Original-site:  http://www.calno.com/evilvte/
Copying-policy: GPL-2
Size:		20K
Extension_by:   Arslan S.
Comments:	Keybindings:
		----------------------------
		copy:		ctrl+shift+c
		paste:		ctlr+shift+v
		select all:	ctlr+shift+s
		add tab:	ctlr+shift+t
		remove tab:	ctlr+shift+w
		next tab:	ctlr+shift+a
		previous tab:	ctlr+shift+z
		----------------------------
		
		Toggle background order: "No background", "Transparent", "Image"

		Background image path: ~/.config/evilvte/background.png

		This extension is PPI compatible.
